title: modin.pandas.Series.set_axis | Snowflake Documentation
paragraphs: Assign desired index to given axis.
labels (list-like, Index, MultiIndex) – The values for the new index.

axis ({index (0), rows(0)}, default 0) – Axis for the function to be applied on.
For Series this parameter is unused and defaults to 0.
copy (bool, default True) – this parameter is unused.
